The first table only gives information about the analysis window (which
will be the same for all individuals):

```{ .sh .codeL }
destrat out/coh-nrem.db +PSI -r F
```
```
ID     F    F1    F2   NF
F01    3     1     5    9
F01    5     3     7    9
F01    7     5     9    9
F01    9     7    11    9
